  "title": "F&B Management Trainee (Hot Kitchen)",
  "description": "<h1><strong>🥐 Passion Is Our Main Ingredient🥐</strong></h1><p><strong>Baker & Cook Singapore </strong>- Singapore’s only true artisan bakery & foodstore is hiring!</p><h3>💰 <strong>** Attractive Sign-on Bonus**</strong>💰</h3><p>✅ Singaporean* | Singapore PR* | PLOC</p><p>✅ 6 Days Work Week</p><p>🚫 No quota available</p><p><br /></p><p><strong>🍕 Outlets: Asian Civilizations Museum </strong>| <strong>Café Carrera by Baker & Cook (Guoco Midtown) | Café Carrera by Baker & Cook (Jewel) | Chip Bee Garden | Dairy Farm | Dempsey | Eng Kong Park | Hillcrest | Namly Place | South Bouna Vista | Serangoon Garden | Swan Lake | Sunset Way</strong></p><p><br /></p><p><strong>Job Description</strong></p><ul><li>Oversee and hands-on involvement in daily kitchen operations</li><li>Oversee inventory, ordering and wastage</li><li>Maintain highest quality and consistent products standards</li><li>Ensure safe and proper use of equipment at all times</li><li>Maintain a high standard of cleanliness in and around workstation and strictly abide with health/sanitation regulations</li><li>Assist kitchen managers and chefs in ensuring tasks are completed in a timely manner, and adhering to kitchen workflow</li><li>Any other ad-hoc duties base on operational needs</li></ul><p><br /></p><p><strong>Requirements</strong></p><ul><li>Certificate in Culinary Skills or its equivalent</li><li>Preferably 1 year supervisory experience in a kitchen specialising in Western cuisine</li><li>Good team player and self-motivated</li><li>Able to work on weekends/public holidays</li><li>Split shift required (3 - 6pm)</li></ul><p><br /></p><p><strong>Benefits</strong></p><ul><li><br /></li><li>Various Allowances**</li><li>Medical + Dental benefits</li><li>Birthday vouchers</li><li>Staff discounts across brands</li><li>Company insurance</li><li>Free Staff Meals</li></ul><p><br /></p><p>Interested party may apply via https://forms.gle/G1q4e4nDrfW1yDmL7</p><p>** T&C applies</p>",
